* Done\n96\t\n97\tAdded to `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/db.ts`:\n98\t- `WinStreaks` interface: `{ current: number, best: number }`\n99\t- `getWinStreaks(wallet)` method on `Db` interface\n100\t- Implementation: SQL query groups `transactions` by `match_id`, uses `bool_or(tx_type = 'payout')` and `bool_or(tx_type = 'deposit')` to determine win/loss per match, orders by `MAX(created_at) DESC`. Application code walks the ordered results: counts consecutive wins from most recent for `current`, tracks longest run for `best`. Refund-only matches (no deposit, no payout) are skipped. If no losses encountered, current = total streak.\n101\t- Verified: `pnpm lint` (0 errors, 1 existing warning) and `pnpm typecheck` both pass\n102\t\n103\t## Iteration 18 — 2026-03-31T15:07:24Z — OK\n104\t- **Log**: iteration-018.log\n105\t\n106\t## Iteration 19 — Per-game breakdown query\n107\t\n108\t**Item:** `[engine] Per-game breakdown query`\n109\t**Status:** Done\n110\t\n111\tAdded to `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/db.ts`:\n112\t- `GameBreakdownStats` interface: `{ gamesPlayed: number, totalWagered: bigint, totalWins: number, winRate: number, netPnl: bigint }`\n113\t- `getGameBreakdown(wallet)` method on `Db` interface + implementation\n114\t- SQL: same aggregation as `getPlayerStats` but with `GROUP BY game`\n115\t- Maps DB game names to frontend names: `lord` → `lord-of-rngs`, `closecall` → `close-call`, `coinflip` → `coinflip`\n116\t- Games with zero `gamesPlayed` are omitted from the result\n117\t- Verified: `pnpm lint` (0 errors, 1 existing warning) and `pnpm typecheck` both pass\n118\t\n119\t## Iteration 19 — 2026-03-31T15:11:18Z — OK\n120\t- **Log**: iteration-019.log\n121\t\n122\t## Iteration 20 — GET /profile/me endpoint\n123\t\n124\t**Item:** `[engine] GET /profile/me endpoint`\n125\t**Status:** Done\n126\t\n127\tAdded `GET /me` handler to `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/routes/profile.ts`:\n128\t- Gets wallet fr