{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PWHsaK556RDDh4b1wd7yam","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information. Let me compile the full report:\n\n## Summary of Player Stats DB Functions and Types\n\nBased on my analysis of `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/db.ts`, here are the complete implementations:\n\n---\n\n### **Type Definitions** (Lines 198-223)\n\n#### `PlayerStats` Interface (Lines 198-204)\n```typescript\nexport interface PlayerStats {\n  gamesPlayed: number;\n  totalWagered: bigint;\n  totalWins: number;\n  winRate: number;\n  netPnl: bigint;\n}\n```\n\n#### `PublicPlayerStats` Interface (Lines 206-210)\n```typescript\nexport interface PublicPlayerStats {\n  gamesPlayed: number;\n  totalWins: number;\n  winRate: number;\n}\n```\n\n#### `WinStreaks` Interface (Lines 212-215)\n```typescript\nexport interface WinStreaks {\n  current: number;\n  best: number;\n}\n```\n\n#### `GameBreakdownStats` Interface (Lines 217-223)\n```typescript\nexport interface GameBreakdownStats {\n  gamesPlayed: number;\n  totalWagered: bigint;\n  totalWins: number;\n  winRate: number;\n  netPnl: bigint;\n}\n```\n\n#### Transaction Types (Lines 102-125)\n```typescript\nexport type TransactionType = \"deposit\" | \"payout\" | \"refund\";\n\nexport interface Transaction {\n  id: string;\n  wallet: string;\n  game: string;\n  match_id: string;\n  tx_type: TransactionType;\n  amount_lamports: number;\n  tx_sig: string;\n  created_at: Date;\n}\n\nexport interface InsertTransactionParams {\n  wallet: string;\n  game: string;\n  matchId: string;\n  txType: TransactionType;\n  amountLamports: number;\n  txSig: string;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Function Implementations**\n\n#### `getPlayerStats(wallet: string): Promise<PlayerStats>` (Lines 1162-1193)\n```typescript\nasync getPlayerStats(wallet) {\n  const rows = await sql<\n    Array<{\n      games_played: string;\n      total_wagered: string;\n      total_wins: string;\n      net_pnl: string;\n    }>\n  >`\n    SELECT\n      COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN tx_type = 'deposit' THEN match_id END)::text AS games_played,\n      COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN tx_type = 'deposit' THEN amount_lamports ELSE 0 END), 0)::text AS total_wagered,\n      COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN tx_type = 'payout' THEN match_id END)::text AS total_wins,\n      COALESCE(\n        SUM(CASE WHEN tx_type IN ('payout', 'refund') THEN amount_lamports\n                 WHEN tx_type = 'deposit' THEN -amount_lamports\n                 ELSE 0 END),\n        0\n      )::text AS net_pnl\n    FROM transactions\n    WHERE wallet = ${wallet}\n  `;\n  const row = rows[0]!;\n  const gamesPlayed = Number(row.games_played);\n  const totalWins = Number(row.total_wins);\n  return {\n    gamesPlayed,\n    totalWagered: BigInt(row.total_wagered),\n    totalWins,\n    winRate: gamesPlayed > 0 ? totalWins / gamesPlayed : 0,\n    netPnl: BigInt(row.net_pnl),\n  };\n}\n```\n\n**Key Logic:**\n- Games played: COUNT of DISTINCT match_ids with 'deposit' transactions\n- Total wagered: SUM of all 'deposit' amounts in lamports\n- Total wins: COUNT of DISTINCT match_ids with 'payout' transactions\n- Net PnL: Sum of all payouts/refunds minus deposits\n- Win rate: totalWins / gamesPlayed (0 if no games played)\n\n---\n\n#### `getPublicPlayerStats(wallet: string): Promise<PublicPlayerStats>` (Lines 1196-1202)\n```typescript\nasync getPublicPlayerStats(wallet) {\n  const full = await this.getPlayerStats(wallet);\n  return {\n    gamesPlayed: full.gamesPlayed,\n    totalWins: full.totalWins,\n    winRate: full.winRate,\n  };\n}\n```\n\n**Purpose:** Returns a public-safe subset of player stats (excludes `totalWagered` and `netPnl`)\n\n---\n\n#### `getGameBreakdown(wallet: string): Promise<Record<string, GameBreakdownStats>>` (Lines 1205-1251)\n```typescript\nasync getGameBreakdown(wallet) {\n  const DB_TO_FRONTEND: Record<string, string> = {\n    coinflip: \"coinflip\",\n    lord: \"lord-of-rngs\",\n    closecall: \"close-call\",\n  };\n\n  const rows = await sql<\n    Array<{\n      game: string;\n      games_played: string;\n      total_wagered: string;\n      total_wins: string;\n      net_pnl: string;\n    }>\n  >`\n    SELECT\n      game,\n      COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN tx_type = 'deposit' THEN match_id END)::text AS games_played,\n      COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN tx_type = 'deposit' THEN amount_lamports ELSE 0 END), 0)::text AS total_wagered,\n      COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN tx_type = 'payout' THEN match_id END)::text AS total_wins,\n      COALESCE(\n        SUM(CASE WHEN tx_type IN ('payout', 'refund') THEN amount_lamports\n                 WHEN tx_type = 'deposit' THEN -amount_lamports\n                 ELSE 0 END),\n        0\n      )::text AS net_pnl\n    FROM transactions\n    WHERE wallet = ${wallet}\n    GROUP BY game\n  `;\n\n  const result: Record<string, GameBreakdownStats> = {};\n  for (const row of rows) {\n    const gamesPlayed = Number(row.games_played);\n    if (gamesPlayed === 0) continue;\n    const totalWins = Number(row.total_wins);\n    const frontendName = DB_TO_FRONTEND[row.game] ?? row.game;\n    result[frontendName] = {\n      gamesPlayed,\n      totalWagered: BigInt(row.total_wagered),\n      totalWins,\n      winRate: gamesPlayed > 0 ? totalWins / gamesPlayed : 0,\n      netPnl: BigInt(row.net_pnl),\n    };\n  }\n  return result;\n}\n```\n\n**Key Logic:**\n- Same aggregation as `getPlayerStats` but grouped by `game`\n- Skips games with zero activity\n- Maps DB game names (`coinflip`, `lord`, `closecall`) to frontend names (`coinflip`, `lord-of-rngs`, `close-call`)\n- Returns Record keyed by frontend game names\n\n---\n\n#### `getWinStreaks(wallet: string): Promise<WinStreaks>` (Lines 1254-1296)\n```typescript\nasync getWinStreaks(wallet) {\n  // Get outcome per match ordered by most recent first.\n  // A match with a 'payout' row = win, 'deposit' without 'payout' = loss,\n  // only 'refund' = skip (excluded).\n  const rows = await sql<\n    Array<{ match_id: string; has_payout: boolean; has_deposit: boolean }>\n  >`\n    SELECT\n      match_id,\n      bool_or(tx_type = 'payout') AS has_payout,\n      bool_or(tx_type = 'deposit') AS has_deposit\n    FROM transactions\n    WHERE wallet = ${wallet}\n    GROUP BY match_id\n    HAVING bool_or(tx_type = 'deposit') OR bool_or(tx_type = 'payout')\n    ORDER BY MAX(created_at) DESC\n  `;\n\n  let current = 0;\n  let best = 0;\n  let streak = 0;\n  let currentSet = false;\n\n  for (const row of rows) {\n    // Skip refund-only matches (no deposit, no payout)\n    if (!row.has_deposit && !row.has_payout) continue;\n\n    const isWin = row.has_payout;\n    if (isWin) {\n      streak++;\n      if (streak > best) best = streak;\n    } else {\n      if (!currentSet) {\n        current = streak;\n        currentSet = true;\n      }\n      streak = 0;\n    }\n  }\n  // If we never hit a loss, current streak = total streak\n  if (!currentSet) current = streak;\n\n  return { current, best };\n}\n```\n\n**Key Logic:**\n- Queries all matches grouped by match_id with booleans for `has_payout` and `has_deposit`\n- Orders by most recent first\n- Iterates through matches (most recent first):\n  - **Win** (has_payout): increment streak, update best if needed\n  - **Loss** (no payout but has deposit): set current streak if not already set, reset streak to 0\n- `current`: current consecutive wins from most recent match\n- `best`: longest winning streak ever\n\n---\n\n#### `insertTransaction(params: InsertTransactionParams): Promise<void>` (Lines 811-824)\n```typescript\nasync insertTransaction(params) {\n  await sql`\n    INSERT INTO transactions (wallet, game, match_id, tx_type, amount_lamports, tx_sig)\n    VALUES (\n      ${params.wallet},\n      ${params.game},\n      ${params.matchId},\n      ${params.txType},\n      ${params.amountLamports},\n      ${params.txSig}\n    )\n    ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING\n  `;\n}\n```\n\n**Key Details:**\n- `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING`: Idempotent - ignores duplicate inserts\n\n---\n\n#### `insertTransactions(params: InsertTransactionParams[]): Promise<void>` (Lines 826-840)\n```typescript\nasync insertTransactions(params) {\n  if (params.length === 0) return;\n  const values = params.map((p) => ({\n    wallet: p.wallet,\n    game: p.game,\n    match_id: p.matchId,\n    tx_type: p.txType,\n    amount_lamports: p.amountLamports,\n    tx_sig: p.txSig,\n  }));\n  await sql`\n    INSERT INTO transactions ${sql(values, \"wallet\", \"game\", \"match_id\", \"tx_type\", \"amount_lamports\", \"tx_sig\")}\n    ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING\n  `;\n}\n```\n\n**Key Details:**\n- Bulk insert multiple transactions\n- Handles empty array case early (returns without executing query)\n- Uses parametrized bulk insert with `sql(values, ...columns)` syntax\n- Also uses `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING` for idempotency"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cd479181-9c0f-4c58-8b77-ba63a57dd2e1","uuid":"cf000daf-2af8-4035-afb5-bbcd64c44d38","timestamp":"2026-03-31T15:27:10.919Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"I need to understand the DB functions for player stats in this project. Search for and read the following functions in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/db.ts`:\n1. `getPlayerStats` \n2. `getWinStreaks`\n3. `getGameBreakdown`\n4. `getPublicPlayerStats`\n5. `insertUserTransaction`\n\nAlso find the `PlayerStats`, `PublicPlayerStats`, `WinStreaks`, `GameBreakdownStats` type definitions in db.ts.\n\nReport the full implementation of each function and type definition, including their signatures and SQL queries.","agentId":"a36eb4a8010b95dbc","agentType":"Explore","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information. Let me compile the full report:\n\n## Summary of Player Stats DB Functions and Types\n\nBased on my analysis of `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/db.ts`, here are the complete implementations:\n\n---\n\n### **Type Definitions** (Lines 198-223)\n\n#### `PlayerStats` Interface (Lines 198-204)\n```typescript\nexport interface PlayerStats {\n  gamesPlayed: number;\n  totalWagered: bigint;\n  totalWins: number;\n  winRate: number;\n  netPnl: bigint;\n}\n```\n\n#### `PublicPlayerStats` Interface (Lines 206-210)\n```typescript\nexport interface PublicPlayerStats {\n  gamesPlayed: number;\n  totalWins: number;\n  winRate: number;\n}\n```\n\n#### `WinStreaks` Interface (Lines 212-215)\n```typescript\nexport interface WinStreaks {\n  current: number;\n  best: number;\n}\n```\n\n#### `GameBreakdownStats` Interface (Lines 217-223)\n```typescript\nexport interface GameBreakdownStats {\n  gamesPlayed: number;\n  totalWagered: bigint;\n  totalWins: number;\n  winRate: number;\n  netPnl: bigint;\n}\n```\n\n#### Transaction Types (Lines 102-125)\n```typescript\nexport type TransactionType = \"deposit\" | \"payout\" | \"refund\";\n\nexport interface Transaction {\n  id: string;\n  wallet: string;\n  game: string;\n  match_id: string;\n  tx_type: TransactionType;\n  amount_lamports: number;\n  tx_sig: string;\n  created_at: Date;\n}\n\nexport interface InsertTransactionParams {\n  wallet: string;\n  game: string;\n  matchId: string;\n  txType: TransactionType;\n  amountLamports: number;\n  txSig: string;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Function Implementations**\n\n#### `getPlayerStats(wallet: string): Promise<PlayerStats>` (Lines 1162-1193)\n```typescript\nasync getPlayerStats(wallet) {\n  const rows = await sql<\n    Array<{\n      games_played: string;\n      total_wagered: string;\n      total_wins: string;\n      net_pnl: string;\n    }>\n  >`\n    SELECT\n      COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN tx_type = 'deposit' THEN match_id END)::text AS games_played,\n      COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN tx_type = 'deposit' THEN amount_lamports ELSE 0 END), 0)::text AS total_wagered,\n      COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN tx_type = 'payout' THEN match_id END)::text AS total_wins,\n      COALESCE(\n        SUM(CASE WHEN tx_type IN ('payout', 'refund')