nt, amount_lamports, side, match_id, phase, entries)\n        VALUES (\n          ${params.pda},\n          ${params.game},\n          ${params.creator},\n          ${params.serverKey},\n          ${params.secret},\n          ${params.commitment},\n          ${params.amountLamports},\n          ${params.side},\n          ${params.matchId},\n          ${params.phase},\n          ${params.entries ? sql.json(params.entries) : null}\n        )\n        RETURNING *\n      `;\n      return normalizeRound(rows[0]!);\n    },","numLines":30,"startLine":575,"totalLines":1309}}}
